Text:
Includes-
The Boys 1-71
Butcher, Baker... 1-4
Herogasm 1-6
Highland Laddie 1-6
and a Tek Knight .rar

Thanks for putting it all together, gordo!
So, everything but the last issue...

Personally, I am just going to call #71 the 'Final' issue and get on with my life. I will just leave it to my imagination rather than read some BS epilogue which will, no doubt, pimp some sort of sequel.

'THE BOYS' IS FINISHED!!! YAY!!!
